name: Geb
title: Geb - God of the Earth | Egyptian Mythology
subtitle: God of the Earth
shortDescription: Geb is the earth god, depicted lying beneath his sister-consort Nut (sky). Father of Osiris , Isis , Set , and Nephthys . His laughter causes earthquakes, and vegetation grows from his body. As earth god, he judged disputes between Horus and Set , ultimately awarding rulership to Horus .
